{
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/:path*", "destination": "/site/:path*" }
  ],
  "cleanUrls": true
}
```

This catches **all routes** and maps them to `/site/`

Result:
- `vexura.io/` → `/site/index.html`
- `vexura.io/tool` → `/site/tool.html`
- `vexura.io/marketplace` → `/site/marketplace.html`
